FMC Corp said it will consider sellingto the public a minority interest in a subsidiary that willhold the company's North American gold and precious metalsproperties and operations.    FMC said its board also authorized the transfer of themetals properties to the newly formed unit.    An unnamed investment advisor has been retained to help inevaluating alternatives on the properties, which consist of awholly owned gold mine at Paradise Peak, Nev., a 30 pctinterest in a gold mine at Jerritt Canyon, Nev., and a 28 pctinterest in a gold mine near Austin, Nev. Reuter&#3;